window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ruwen and his friends have five days to spring a comrade from the world’s most secure prison, Legion’s Vault, located in the city of a god that wants him dead. Permanently dead.</p> <p>Their only way into the city is competing in the yearly Step Championship. Nothing says low profile like combat in front of a hundred thousand spectators.</p> <p>If remaining anonymous and breaking into a legendary prison didn’t already spell disaster, an old acquaintance appears. One who knows Ruwen’s name and face and can destroy all their plans.</p> <p>Entering the fifth level of Legion’s Vault seems difficult, but leaving might prove impossible.</p> <p>Because the path home has a cost and will condemn one of them to certain death.</p>"; 
